===Noun===
'''phoney'''
# '''1902''' A person who professes beliefs or opinions that he or she does not hold or assumes an identity other than their own.
#:''He claims to be a doctor, but he's nothing but a fast-talking '''phoney'''.''

====Synonyms====
*[[dissember]]
*[[pretender]]
*[[fake]]

